 > http://www.google.com/design/spec/style/color.html#color-ui-color-palette

 > Create color theme based on uploaded image: > http://pictaculous.com/

 > Color Converter rgba > rgb > http://yolijn.com/convert-rgba-to-rgb

 1. Primary (JQM: a)
